---
import PolicyLayout from '../layouts/PolicyLayout.astro';
---

<PolicyLayout title="Terms of Use" lastUpdated="01/05/2026">

  <section class="mb-8">
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      The full and current Terms of Use governing access to and use of XOS — Keane International Legal Consultancy LLP's Cross-Border Compliance Operating System — are maintained inside the XOS application itself, where they can be reviewed in your preferred language and accepted at the point of subscription or partner onboarding.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-dark mb-3">Where to find the Terms</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Open <a href="https://xos.kilc.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-accent hover:underline">xos.kilc.co.uk</a> and follow the <strong>Terms of Use</strong> link in the footer. The Terms cover, among other things:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-4">
      <li>Definitions and interpretation</li>
      <li>Subscriptions, fees, and the 14-day cooling-off period under the Consumer Contracts Regulations 2013</li>
      <li>Acceptable use and intellectual property</li>
      <li>Compliance content disclaimers (XOS provides general regulatory intelligence, not legal advice)</li>
      <li>Limitations of liability and indemnities</li>
      <li>Data protection under UK GDPR and the Data Protection Act 2018</li>
      <li>Data residency and transfers (including PIPL considerations for Chinese institutional partners)</li>
      <li>Term, termination, and dispute resolution under English law</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Material changes to the Terms are announced to subscribers by email at least 30 days before they take effect, with the version number and effective date clearly marked.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-8">
    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-dark mb-3">Quick contacts</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-4">
      <li><strong>General enquiries:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@kilc.co.uk" class="text-brand-accent hover:underline">info@kilc.co.uk</a></li>
      <li><strong>Legal notices:</strong> <a href="mailto:legal@kilc.co.uk" class="text-brand-accent hover:underline">legal@kilc.co.uk</a></li>
      <li><strong>Data protection:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@kilc.co.uk" class="text-brand-accent hover:underline">privacy@kilc.co.uk</a></li>
      <li><strong>Compliance matters:</strong> <a href="mailto:compliance@kilc.co.uk" class="text-brand-accent hover:underline">compliance@kilc.co.uk</a></li>
      <li><strong>Registered address:</strong> Keane International Legal Consultancy LLP, 128 City Road, London EC1V 2NX, United Kingdom</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

</PolicyLayout>
